^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|First, let me discuss the play and second hand low. As you know, second hand low is virtually always right. The rationale behind second hand low is you want your honors to capture the opponents honors. This hand was unusual, in that Kim can violate second hand low in 2 different suits. |
